[section#container.node.dtor
    [:en] Destructor
    [:zh_CN] 析构函数
]

[codeblock:declaration]
constexpr ~[[redoc("^>")]]node-handle();
[codeblock:end]

[div:description]
[para:effects]
[:en] If [`[*ptr_] != nullptr] is [`true], destroys the [`value_type] subobject
in the [*container-node-type] object pointed to by [*ptr_] by calling
[`[*ator-traits]::destroy], then deallocates [*ptr_] by calling
[`[*ator-traits]::template rebind_traits<[*container-node-type]>::deallocate].
[:zh_CN] 如果 [`[*ptr_] != nullptr] 为 [`true]，则通过调用 [`[*ator-traits]::destroy]
来销毁 [*ptr_] 所指向的 [*container-node-type] 对象中的 [`value_type] 子对象，然后通过
调用 [`[*ator-traits]::template rebind_traits<container_node_type>::deallocate]
来回收 [*ptr_]。
[div:end]
